      "message": "Line 2070: Messages without a plugin-generated bodyOverwrite are treated as permanently missing, so loadMissingBodyOverwrites() will re-run plugin transforms for the same loaded history on every load/reload. On large conversations this can repeatedly invoke plugins over the full history even when there is no overwrite to produce. Store an explicit processed/no-overwrite state, or transform only the newly loaded range.\n```suggestion\n// Track that this message was already processed even when no overwrite was produced.\nrealIt-\u003esecond-\u003epluginData[\"bodyOverwriteProcessed\"] \u003d \"true\";\n```\nThen include that marker in the needsWork check and clear it in reloadBodyOverwriteMessages().",
